  "body": "Reduce bonsai storage in lightweight mode by not storing the tree state nodes as these require a lot of storage.\n\nTasks\n* Change Bonsai storage to not write to the TRIE_BRANCH_STORAGE\n* Change Bonsai storage so that data cannot be read from the TRIE_BRANCH_STORAGE\n* Change state root calculation so it becomes a no op when using bonsai light\n* Disable the state root verification when in bonsai light mode",
